title: A conversation with OpenAI’s CEO, Sam Altman | Hosted by UCL
description:
This recording is of a fireside chat with OpenAI's CEO, Sam Altman that took place on 24 May 2023. 

OpenAI is an AI research and deployment company. OpenAI’s mission is to create safe and powerful AI that benefits all of humanity. Learn more at openai.com

UCL - London's Global University was founded in 1826 and is London's Global University. It is consistently ranked among the top 10 universities in the world and is one of only a handful of institutions rated as having the strongest academic reputation and the broadest research impact. Learn more at ucl.ac.uk
